Step-by-step install php v5.3.3-48

1.  Cek list version php di centos 6
    # yum list php
2.  Install php 
    # yum install php
3.  Install php for postgresql
    # yum install php-pgsql
4.  Cek version php
    # php --version
3.  Restart httpd
    # service httpd restart
4.  Cek version php melalui localhost, buat file baru
    # nano /var/www/html/info.php
    Isikan code php ini, lalu save  
    <?php
      phpinfo();
    ?>
5.  Akses localhost sekarang maka akan muncul info php yang telah diinstall : http://localhost/info.php


Note: 
Menggati environment php -v :
- alias php=/usr/bin/php (php v5.3)
- alias php=/opt/lampp/bin/php (php v5.6)

Selesai, silahkan coba ditesting

